name: S%27Ten_Gali_Ak%27Ar
content: S'Ten Gali Ak'Ar was the Gorothite leader of the Gor'Jen'Ar resistance movement on Goroth Prime. A philosopher by nature, she became a warrior and politician in exile to lead the Gor'Jen'Ar resistance movement. Relying on false identities, S'Ten Gali Ak'Ar lived among the people of Graith.
